Package space.sunqian.common.base.system

Class SystemKeys

java.lang.Object
space.sunqian.common.base.system.SystemKeys
public class SystemKeys extends Object
Provides keys of system properties in SystemKit.getProperties(). Most of them are standard keys which always have values, but some are not.
See Also:
  • System.getProperties()
  • System.getProperty(String)
